{"tid":1692072,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"良心公司JYP TWICE的行程已經排到2021年","createTime":"2019-11-04T02:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T06:34:00.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0cf434ccf3a00b3aa242b1f65beeae4ebec47d17","tid":1692072,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:18:31.000Z","msg":"1日是TWICE定延生日，在VLIVE直播了兩個小時，志效後來拿著蛋糕驚喜登場。隨後兩人開始對話，談到TWICE的行程。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n志效一邊查看行程，一邊說：「我好奇一件事，我們行程不是會定下來嘛，究竟現在定好的行程會排到幾月？」定延：「我也好奇！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n志效：「現在來看看，2020年4月有，5月有，6月也有。怎麼做到定得那麼詳細的？細緻到這種程度，難道不是今年嗎？7月、8月... 哇，排到了2021年1月。」定延：「沒有細節，但確實定下來了。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對此粉絲紛紛留言：「現在只求九兔完整就好」、「公司讓她們多休息吧」等。<br />\n<br />\n唔知下一個到邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0c1046678956ad13a27db311e174b6a157d8ab","tid":1692072,"uid":229026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:22:50.000Z","msg":"猩猩想做死班女咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550f64b6ee9e90e4a53ab7e344c2e4ea816419d0","tid":1692072,"uid":33359,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:22:51.000Z","msg":"下年定延宣布退團返屋企幫我凑仔"},{"pid":"0d641526380dcb844de3d9e8bed12c5b0e1269f6","tid":1692072,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:25:06.000Z","msg":"姜丹去死 隊長魚仔跟我"},{"pid":"59eb558a0f5726ce6fc5cbb9ab7d8aef156dd523","tid":1692072,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"550f64b6ee9e90e4a53ab7e344c2e4ea816419d0","tid":1692072,"uid":33359,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:22:51.000Z","msg":"下年定延宣布退團返屋企幫我凑仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:26:50.000Z","msg":"下年有得湊既話 你應該戴綠帽"},{"pid":"13b5038ba1744467bb647c96a6c502de0d9beec4","tid":1692072,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"550f64b6ee9e90e4a53ab7e344c2e4ea816419d0","tid":1